Package think.rpgitems.power.impl

Class PowerRumble

  • java.lang.Object
    • think.rpgitems.power.impl.BasePower
      • think.rpgitems.power.impl.PowerRumble
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Power, PowerRightClick
    public class PowerRumble
extends BasePower
implements PowerRightClick
    Power rumble.

    The rumble power sends a shockwave through the ground and sends any hit entities flying with power power. The wave will travel distance blocks.
